codex
The failure is caused by measuring the initial takeoff/settling transient as `flight_error.max_m`: the air-reach node starts about five seconds after the bridge, while the vehicle is still climbing to the bridge’s initial hover target. I’m going to make the live runner wait longer before starting `air_reach_demo`, keeping the existing metric threshold instead of loosening it.
apply patch
